{
  "texts": [
    "Employing AI involves utilizing it for content delivery, crafting personalized learning experiences, and implementing adaptive learning platforms.",
    "This facilitates the customization of educational content according to individual students' needs, enabling them to learn at their own pace, as proposed by [71].",
    "The implementation of AI-powered chatbots and virtual assistants in education started gaining traction during this period.",
    "These tools were used for answering student queries, providing information, and facilitating communication within educational institutions [72,73].",
    "Common AI technologies used in Nigerian education include web tools [66], data mining implementations [41,48], Google Classroom, Zoom, WhatsApp, and blogs [42,73]."
  ]
}